      <p class="font-italic">*Please note an (*) indicates that the club runs for 90 minutes every second week when possible. Due to holidays and or dates of field trips it's not always possible to hold the club every two weeks, however we have spaced them out as best as possible.</p>
      <p>If you want to join simply fill in the online form and book your place. If we reach the minimum participant number required for the clubs, we will run them.</p>
      <p>If you join before the first 7 lessons are over the fee is ¥20000.</p>
      <p>If there are 7 or less club dates left, then the fee will be ¥10000.</p>

      <h2 class="mt-5">Schedule and Transport</h2>

      <p>Students will be supervised while having a snack between the end of classes and the start of the club activity at 15:45. Most clubs finish between 16:30 and 17:15. There will be no buses at this time to transport your child home, so try to carpool with other parents.</p>

